title: Schedule A Tour To See Our Newly Renovated Apartment Homes/Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
